{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "05", "m": "07", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "22", "M": "49", "S": "04"}}, "news": [{"title": "Chandigarh wants to rise higher but can its roads take the load?", "para": "Chandigarh's ambitious development plans, including higher building limits and mixed land use, are raising serious concerns about traffic congestion.  Official reports and resident objections highlight a critical gap: the city is densifying without a clear plan for its overloaded transport infrastructure.  Decades-old warnings about saturated roads and a lack of mass transit are now a stark reality, with private vehicles dominating and speeds plummeting.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/infrastructure/chandigarhs-urban-dilemma-higher-density-vs-traffic-chaos/132191835?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-1679817/132191835.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "infrastructure"}, {"title": "Ludhiana: LIT slashes reserve price to \u20b9182 crore in fresh bid to auction its commercial building", "para": "Ludhiana Improvement Trust has slashed the reserve price of a prime commercial building by \u20b915 crore to \u20b9182 crore in a fresh e-auction, hoping to attract buyers after previous attempts failed. The 18-year-old, abandoned property, featuring extensive commercial space and parking, has suffered from neglect. LIT is also considering price cuts for other properties due to poor market response.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/commercial/ludhiana-improvement-trust-reduces-auction-price-of-prime-commercial-building-to-182-crore/132191743?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-192338/132191743.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "commercial"}, {"title": "Manesar civic body razes six concrete plants, 30 more under scanner", "para": "